{"tid":806894,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係lecture theatre 開左av 好想quit u","createTime":"2018-09-05T05:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T09:29:11.000Z","uid":166948,"like":1301,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"f150c5231b04e692278b86cac5b991b19e0041b2","tid":806894,"uid":166948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"話説上星期黃金單野我已經覺得好撚㭍<br />\n之後個幾日都匿係屋企打J<br />\n所以本來今日食開sem飯 我都唔係幾想去<br />\n但話哂第時上堂住hall都會見到<br />\n所以我都照去 諗住自嘲埋一份扮無事<br />\n點知我遲左少少到啲人已經話咩屯門出黎係耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦廢話唔講<br />\n咁食完飯我地都一齊上堂<br />\n係core 大course<br />\n坐LT 大約2 百幾人啦<br />\n由於啱啱開sem<br />\n好多人部nb都未拎得<br />\n而我一早已經買左mac bk air<br />\n正當我諗住拎出黎上下網<br />\n唔撚記得琴晚先J完 julia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一揭開成個LT 就係julia既呻淫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經即刻閂返<br />\n點知條鬼佬professor 係到笑<br />\n仲話 i think it is from the left corner<br />\n屌你老尾一講呢句二百幾個人頭同時擰過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隔離個組mate 仲即刻指住我黎笑<br />\n宜家成個LT 都知係我<br />\n個professor 仲問我are u ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n組mate仲要po 哂上gp<br />\n宜家真係覺得好柒 好想quit u"},{"pid":"954d16f2b3ea6dffc1ba8cb151b69de3794e563b","tid":806894,"uid":83594,"like":541,"dislike":4,"score":537,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"原來係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1bd012a8b9e6ebbab693bdda6725614abc7065","tid":806894,"uid":134801,"like":127,"dislike":3,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"召喚評分撚"},{"pid":"127317162763535ca7a23962b30fbc1a1797e120","tid":806894,"uid":194606,"like":508,"dislike":3,"score":505,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"8/10<br />\n唔錯，幾好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos